26 November 2015Deputy Minister of Communications, Stella Ndabeni-Abrahams will deliver a keynote address at the 2nd Annual Alfred Nzo communications and media awards on Friday, 27th November 2015 at Maluti Civic Centre, Matatiele, Eastern Cape. The 2nd Annual Alfred Nzo District Municipality Communicators and Media Awards event is aimed at recognizing and encouraging excellence in the district communications system, build and strengthening relations with the media.Members of the media are invited as follows:Date: Friday, 27th November 2015 Time: 17h00 22h00 Venue: Maluti Civic Centre, Matatiele, Eastern CapeRSVP: Ndyebo Kopo Cell: 0834649529 Email: ndyebok@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries: Mzimasi Ngqelu Cell: 0769043557 Email: mzi@doc.gov.zaIssued by Ministry of Communications